Klopp's Dortmund beat Pellegrini's Malaga 3-2 in the 2013 Champions League quarter-finals courtesy of two injury-time goals. For the winner, four Dortmund players were offside.<br />
<br />
&quot;Klopp is used to winning with offside goals,&quot; said Pellegrini. &quot;He beat me against Malaga with a goal seven metres offside. So he cannot complain about anything.&quot;
